\sum_{k=1}^nk^3 = \left(\sum_{k=1}^n k\right)^2
\sum_{k=1}^nk^3 = \left(\sum_{k=1}^n k\right)^2
\sum_{k=1}^nk^3 =\left(\frac{n(n+1)}{2}\right)^2
\sum_{k=1}^n k=\frac{n(n+1)}{2}\to\left(\sum_{k=1}^n k\right)^2=\left(\frac{n(n+1)}{2}\right)^2
