\sum_{k=1}^nk^3 + (n+1)^3= (1+2+\ldots+n+(n+1))^2=\\ \left(\sum_{k=1}^n k\right)^2+2(1+2+\ldots+n)(n+1)+(n+1)^2
(1+2+\ldots+n)=\frac{n(n+1)}{2}
(n+1)^3=2\frac{n(n+1)}{2}(n+1)+(n+1)^2=(n+1)^3\checkmark
